---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About">
  <main id="main">

    <!-- =================== HERO =================== -->
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="eyebrow">About</div>

        <div class="about-hero-grid">
          <h1 class="display">Roha. <em class="italic-accent">A</em> four-letter word that means a lot.</h1>
          <div class="about-hero-side">
            <p class="pull"><em>"A</em> small studio that helps founders and indie makers build digital products that
              feel real."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =================== THE NAME =================== -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="eyebrow">01 — The Name</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Not an acronym, not random.</h2>

        <div class="name-grid">
          <div class="pull">
            <em>"Roha</em> is Batak for heart — a blend of feeling, thought, and intent. Our work tries to do the same:
            quiet on the surface, considered underneath."
          </div>
          <div>
            <p>This name wasn&rsquo;t picked from a naming agency shortlist, or pulled from a generator. Roha is a word
              people from North Sumatra use every day — to describe a feeling, an intention, and a decision in a single
              word.</p>
            <p>For a studio that deals with visual decisions every day, this word feels right. It reminds us: good
              design starts with clear intent. Everything else follows.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="name-card">
          <div class="item">
            <div class="k">Pronounced</div>
            <div class="v">/ˈro.ha/</div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="k">Origin</div>
            <div class="v">Batak Toba</div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="k">Translates to</div>
            <div class="v">Heart · Mind · Soul</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =================== PRINCIPLES =================== -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div class="eyebrow">02 — Principles</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Four things we hold to.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="principles-grid">
          <div class="principle">
            <div class="num">01</div>
            <h3>Quiet on the surface, considered underneath.</h3>
            <p>Design that doesn&rsquo;t shout, but every choice has a reason. Spacing, sizing, color — we can explain
              all of it if you ask.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <div class="num">02</div>
            <h3>Warmth is a discipline.</h3>
            <p>Warmth isn&rsquo;t an accident. It&rsquo;s chosen, measured, intentional. Like a person who&rsquo;s warm
              — not because they forgot to be professional, but because they meant it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <div class="num">03</div>
            <h3>Systems, not decoration.</h3>
            <p>We build design systems, not one pretty page that falls apart on the second update. Components, tokens,
              documentation — so it still feels right a year from now.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <div class="num">04</div>
            <h3>Ship it, don&rsquo;t polish it forever.</h3>
            <p>Shipped &gt; perfect. Better a 1.0 that&rsquo;s live than a 0.9 that&rsquo;s delayed. What matters is
              knowing what to improve in the next iteration.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =================== PROCESS =================== -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div class="eyebrow">03 — Process</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Five steps from brief<br />to handoff.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="process-steps">
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="num">01</div>
            <h4>Briefing</h4>
            <div class="dur">1–2 days</div>
            <p>Discovery call, scope alignment, deliverables. We make sure we understand the problem first — not jump
              straight to a solution.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="num">02</div>
            <h4>Exploration</h4>
            <div class="dur">3–5 days</div>
            <p>Mood board, wireframes, direction. We pick two or three directions to test before committing to one.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="num">03</div>
            <h4>Design</h4>
            <div class="dur">1–3 weeks</div>
            <p>Visual design, prototype, interaction details. The longest phase, with a weekly review rhythm.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="num">04</div>
            <h4>Iteration</h4>
            <div class="dur">1 week</div>
            <p>Revisions, refinement, polish. A big round of revisions, not little ping-pong loops that wear everyone
              out.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="num">05</div>
            <h4>Handoff</h4>
            <div class="dur">1–2 days</div>
            <p>File delivery, documentation, 2 weeks of support. We make sure the dev team has everything they need.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =================== TOOLS =================== -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="eyebrow">04 — Disciplines &amp; Tools</div>

        <div class="tools-grid">
          <div>
            <h3>What we do.</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="services.html#ux">UX Design</a> <span class="tag">From IDR 8M</span></li>
              <li><a href="services.html#ui">UI Design</a> <span class="tag">From IDR 6M</span></li>
              <li><a href="services.html#web">Website Development</a> <span class="tag">From IDR 15M</span></li>
              <li><a href="services.html#landing">Landing Page Development</a> <span class="tag">From IDR 5M</span></li>
              <li><a href="services.html#brand">Brand &amp; Logo Guideline</a> <span class="tag">From IDR 4M</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Tools we use.</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Figma <span class="tag">Design</span></li>
              <li>Framer · Webflow <span class="tag">No-code</span></li>
              <li>Next.js · Astro <span class="tag">Code</span></li>
              <li>Notion <span class="tag">Docs</span></li>
              <li>Linear · Loom <span class="tag">Workflow</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =================== CONTACT =================== -->
    <section class="section" id="contact">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div class="eyebrow">05 — Contact Us</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Let&rsquo;s talk.</h2>
          <p class="section-lede">Send a brief, a Notion link, or just a story. We reply within 1×24 hours (business
            hours).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-grid">

          <!-- FORM -->
          <!-- Note: replace action with a Formspree/Web3Forms endpoint to make the form live.
             Default fallback: mailto. Example Formspree endpoint: https://formspree.io/f/xyzpqrwt -->
          <form class="contact-form" data-contact-form action="mailto:hello@rohaworks.com" method="post"
            enctype="text/plain" novalidate>

            <div class="field-row">
              <div class="field">
                <label for="name">Name</label>
                <input id="name" name="name" type="text" required placeholder="Your name" />
                <span class="field-error">Please enter your name.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input id="email" name="email" type="email" required placeholder="you@email.com" />
                <span class="field-error">Email is not valid.</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="field-row">
              <div class="field">
                <label for="type">Project Type</label>
                <select id="type" name="type" required>
                  <option value="">Pick one</option>
                  <option>UX Design</option>
                  <option>UI Design</option>
                  <option>Website Development</option>
                  <option>Landing Page</option>
                  <option>Branding</option>
                  <option>Other</option>
                </select>
                <span class="field-error">Please pick a project type.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label for="budget">Budget</label>
                <select id="budget" name="budget" required>
                  <option value="">Pick one</option>
                  <option>&lt; IDR 10M</option>
                  <option>IDR 10–30M</option>
                  <option>IDR 30–50M</option>
                  <option>IDR 50M+</option>
                  <option>Not sure yet</option>
                </select>
                <span class="field-error">Please pick a budget range.</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="field">
              <label for="msg">Message</label>
              <textarea id="msg" name="message" required
                placeholder="A short note about your project — timeline, goals, or reference links if you have any."></textarea>
              <span class="field-error">Tell us a bit about your project.</span>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Send Message <span class="arr">→</span></button>
          </form>

          <!-- INFO -->
          <div class="contact-info">
            <div class="contact-info-block">
              <div class="k">Email</div>
              <div class="v"><a href="mailto:hello@rohaworks.com">hello@rohaworks.com</a></div>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-info-block">
              <div class="k">WhatsApp</div>
              <div class="v">
                <!-- Replace [NO_WA] with active WhatsApp number -->
                <a href="https://wa.me/[NO_WA]?text=Hi%20Roha%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20discuss%20a%20project"
                  target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chat on WhatsApp →</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-info-block">
              <div class="k">Location</div>
              <div class="v">Indonesia · Based in Sumatra</div>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-info-block">
              <div class="k">Working Hours</div>
              <div class="v">Mon–Fri, 09:00–17:00 WIB</div>
              <p>We reply within 1×24 hours (business hours).</p>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-info-block">
              <div class="k">Social</div>
              <div class="footer-social" style="margin-top:14px;">
                <a href="[INSTAGRAM_URL]" aria-label="Instagram" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
                    <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="5" />
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4" />
                    <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r=".8" fill="currentColor" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="[DRIBBBLE_URL]" aria-label="Dribbble" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" />
                    <path d="M8 21c1.5-7 3.5-10 6.5-15M3 11c5 0 12 .5 17 6M21 9c-4 1.5-9 3-18 .5" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="[BEHANCE_URL]" aria-label="Behance" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
                    <path d="M3 6h5a3 3 0 010 6H3zM3 12h6a3 3 0 010 6H3zM14 14a3 3 0 116 0v1h-6a3 3 0 003 3M15 7h4" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="[LINKEDIN_URL]" aria-label="LinkedIn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
                    <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3" />
                    <path d="M8 10v7M8 7v.01M12 17v-4a2 2 0 014 0v4M12 10v7" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="[TIKTOK_URL]" aria-label="TikTok" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
                    <path d="M14 4v10a4 4 0 11-4-4M14 4c0 3 2 5 5 5" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Base>
